  "type": "mcq",
  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">Tanya earns $13.50 per hour at her part-time job. When she works <span class=\"italic\">z</span> hours, she earns <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"13 point 5 0 z \"></span> dollars. Which of the following expressions gives the amount, in dollars, Tanya will earn if she works <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"3 z\"></span> hours?</p>\n",
